          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">The </text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-weight:bold; font-style:italic;" translate="true">X–axis units</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> indicate the </text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true">time, angle, or cycles</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">, for the horizontal X–axis.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">The units are set in the </text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true">Active Motion Settings dialog-box. The options are:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Counts" styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true">Counts</link><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">, </text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true">secs (</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-style:normal;" translate="true">seconds</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true">) ; msecs (</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-style:normal;" translate="true">milliseconds</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true">) ;</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true">cycles</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> (machine cycles) ; </text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true">degrees ;</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true">radians</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#ff6600;" /></para>
